育堂已經再唔係我嘅惡夢。到以家結埋婚生埋仔，呢個折磨我嘅病一直無再出現過嘞。<br />\n祝各位早日病除"},{"pid":"67f5840dbf2850756db1e43a062f926b3e444f1c","tid":1148932,"uid":37493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b033885dd7552219d3804206e35dd95a928ba16","tid":1148932,"uid":166682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de4fedda966b193d0b1f4b93f83bf18f15f5933b","tid":1148932,"uid":37493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7a03ab26e95f76e163f8e5edf47faff37c08454","tid":1148932,"uid":166682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T11:16:14.000Z","msg":"我以前大學同學有講過游水醫得好<br />\n不過我唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我細個有過一段時間，好返無嘢後成年後翻發<br />\n香港空氣真係差到辛苦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T11:17:46.000Z","msg":"咁你每日都要吸藥?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T16:44:44.000Z","msg":"早一兩個禮拜就係<br />\n後來慢慢好返<br />\n就無啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:20:54.000Z","msg":"咁都好D 唔洗長期吸"},{"pid":"e045d5b43a47968e952116ff158ec7d651896b1e","tid":1148932,"uid":37493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7ff7c6ab4e0e945f7d04e32dae767d58b9bd688","tid":1148932,"uid":181182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T18:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:22:34.000Z","msg":"我食辣野會咳得好誇張<br />\n踢波有時太chur都會咳一兩聲<br />\n不過就冇he he 聲"},{"pid":"2a2e136fc29f776248d38320222eab3d27ba16dd","tid":1148932,"uid":166682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67f5840dbf2850756db1e43a062f926b3e444f1c","tid":1148932,"uid":37493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b033885dd7552219d3804206e35dd95a928ba16","tid":1148932,"uid":166682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de4fedda966b193d0b1f4b93f83bf18f15f5933b","tid":1148932,"uid":37493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T11:17:46.000Z","msg":"咁你每日都要吸藥?"},"citedB